- **Race conditions:** Operator-driven cutover; OpenClaw is-active check is informational, not a TOCTOU concern at this scope. ✓
- **Rollback safety:** Both runbooks have explicit Rollback sections — Telegram path documents the BotFather rate-limit re-revoke caveat; WhatsApp explicitly NOT rolled back per spec, with cost-of-leaving-deauth-during-rollback rationale. ✓

